                      throws SBSIParseException
DTO for the configuration of an X2 cost function Calling any of the set methods results in persistence of the data by the header file (to disk with the default implementation of an SBSI header file).

Parameters:
name - name of the data file
dfs - time point at which the data will start to be used
st - scale type of cost function
vt - value type of cost function
used - true if the cost function will use this state
interval - time series interval
header - SBSIheader which will persist the data in this DTO
Throws:
SBSIParseException
